@startuml seq-crm-workflow
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title CRM Customer Lifecycle — Create, Tier Progression, Notification

actor Admin
participant "Admin Dashboard" as AdminApp
participant "CustomersAPI\n/api/crm/customers" as CustAPI
participant "CustomerService" as CustSvc
database "PostgreSQL\ncrm.customers" as DB
participant "NotificationDispatcher" as Dispatcher
participant "NotificationsAPI\n/api/notifications" as NotifAPI

== Customer Creation ==

Admin -> AdminApp : Fill customer form
AdminApp -> CustAPI : POST /api/crm/customers\n{ name, email }
CustAPI -> CustSvc : validate and create
CustSvc -> DB : INSERT INTO crm.customers\n(status='active', tier='standard', order_count=0)
DB --> CustSvc : customer record
CustSvc --> CustAPI : created customer
CustAPI --> AdminApp : 201 Created
AdminApp --> Admin : Show success

== Order Event — Tier Recalculation ==

[-> CustSvc : Order completed event\n(customerId, newOrderCount)
CustSvc -> DB : SELECT tier, order_count\nFROM crm.customers WHERE id=?
DB --> CustSvc : current tier='silver',\norder_count=14
CustSvc -> CustSvc : Calculate new tier:\norder_count 15 → 'gold'
CustSvc -> DB : UPDATE crm.customers\nSET tier='gold', order_count=15
DB --> CustSvc : updated

CustSvc -> Dispatcher : Tier changed: silver → gold
Dispatcher -> NotifAPI : POST /api/notifications\n{ recipientId: adminId,\ntype: 'crm',\nmessage: 'Customer upgraded to Gold' }
NotifAPI --> Dispatcher : 201 Created

@enduml
